<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/meetings/" title="Food and Wine">
<div class="slideText">
<h4>Food and Wine</h4>
<p>When you’re looking for banquet halls in Vancouver, consider Il Centro. Our on-site chef creates exceptional menus that make your event memorable. </p>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="cycle-slide">
<div class="slideImage">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/east-van-green/shop/" title="Shop - Il Centro to go">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/lasagna15.jpg"/>
</a>
</div>
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/east-van-green/shop/" title="Shop - Il Centro to go">
<div class="slideText">
<h4>Shop - Il Centro to go</h4>
<p>Enjoy delicious, high quality Italian food products that are handcrafted daily by our talented in house chefs. No need to sacrifice quality for time when you can have both with our countless take out options available today.</p>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="cycle-slide">
<div class="slideImage">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/learn/" title="Learn Italian with Us">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Botticelli-primavera.jpg"/>
</a>
</div>
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/learn/" title="Learn Italian with Us">
<div class="slideText">
<h4>Learn Italian with Us</h4>
<p>We offer a broad range of fun, instructive Italian classes for all ages and abilities. Our Italian School brings the language to life for kids and adults. </p>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="cycle-slide">
<div class="slideImage">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/events/" title="Immerse Yourself in Italian Culture">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/ilcentro-2.jpg"/>
</a>
</div>
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/events/" title="Immerse Yourself in Italian Culture">
<div class="slideText">
<h4>Immerse Yourself in Italian Culture</h4>
<p>At Il Centro, we partner with some of our city’s most celebrated arts organizations, to proudly showcase visiting Italian artists, musicians, designers, and visiting arts and cultural organizations. </p>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="cycle-slide">
<div class="slideImage">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/events/" title="Discover our Heritage Museum">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/ilcentro-4.jpg"/>
</a>
</div>
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/events/" title="Discover our Heritage Museum">
<div class="slideText">
<h4>Discover our Heritage Museum</h4>
<p>At Il Museo, our on-site museum, we proudly present insightful exhibitions throughout the year, inspired by and celebrating Italian culture. </p>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="cycle-slide">
<div class="slideImage">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/about-us/a-new-vision-for-il-centro/" title="A NEW VISION">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/150910_icc_ideas-fair_913x2705.png"/>
</a>
</div>
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/about-us/a-new-vision-for-il-centro/" title="A NEW VISION">
<div class="slideText">
<h4>A NEW VISION</h4>
<p>What could the future of the Centre be? Tell us what you think!</p>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="cycle-slide">
<div class="slideImage">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/about-us/community-initiatives-engagement/" title="EAST VAN GREEN">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/East-Van-Web-banner-final.jpg"/>
</a>
</div>
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/about-us/community-initiatives-engagement/" title="EAST VAN GREEN">
<div class="slideText">
<h4>EAST VAN GREEN</h4>
<p>A series of projects and programs that connect our community garden, urban farm partnership, farmers’ market, zero waste initiative, <br/>
urban creek restoration, and food literacy and education activities at Il Centro.</p>
</div>
</a>
