<section class="post_content">
<div class="homeMenu">
<a href="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/meetings/"><div class="homeMenuEntry" style="background:#bbbe29;">Request a Booking<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/themes/icc-main/library/images/homeArrow.png" style="float:right; margin-right:2px;"/></div></a>
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/upcoming-events/" title="Il Centro Event Calendar"><div class="homeMenuEntry" style="background:#00b3e3;">Find a Cultural Event<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/themes/icc-main/library/images/homeArrow.png" style="float:right;"/></div></a>
<a href="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/school/"><div class="homeMenuEntry" style="background:#f48120;">Find an Italian Class<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/themes/icc-main/library/images/homeArrow.png" style="float:right;"/></div></a>
</div>
<div class="homeContent">
<h1 class="page-title"> Italian Cultural Centre of Vancouver </h1>
<p>Il Centro is a proud destination for a wide range of community and cultural events in Vancouver. We are also one of the most popular banquet halls in the city, catering for meetings, weddings and receptions. Looking for things to do in Vancouver? Visit Il Centro and discover our wealth of services and our breadth of activities.</p>
</div>
<div class="homeMenu">
<div class="cycle-slideshow noHeight" data-cycle-fx="fade" data-cycle-slides="> div.promote" data-cycle-timeout="2000" data-cycle-speed="2000" data-cycle-pager=".example-pager" data-cycle-log=false>
 
<div class="promote">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/blog/events/il-centro-fundraising-gala-2016/" title="Il Centro Fundrasing Gala">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/FG-2016.png" alt="Fundraising Gala" style="margin-top:-5px;"/>
</a>
</div>
<div class="promote">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/about-us/a-new-vision-for-il-centro/" title="Il Centro Vision">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/il-centro-vision2.jpg" alt="Vision for Il Centro" style="margin-top:-5px;"/>
</a>
</div>
<div class="promote">
<a href="http://italianculturalcentre.ca/about-us/the-italian-card/" title="The Italian Card">
<img src="https://italianculturalcentre.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/italian-card.jpg" alt="The Italian Card" style="margin-top:-5px;"/>
</a>
</div>
 
</div>
</div>
 
